title: Trains - Working On The Railroad^D^
description:
Have you ever passed a track gang and wondered what all those machines actually do? You'll visit a tie replacement and surfacing gang to witness the amazing paradeas it progresses down the track. You will see how coal hoppers are built. All in all a great movie showing you the different aspects of railroading, that most people don't see..

Enjoy


More RR movies to come

The next one is called At The Throttle
